{"tid":906643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［丁撚死人］高明：一旦取消關係法，港股隨時暴升3340點，接近重上三萬點","createTime":"2018-11-18T07:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T11:02:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"76b30fb4726fb947a7f793b328dc05a3bf7660bf","tid":906643,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"【名家搶先睇】取消香港關係法 標普恐見個位數（高明）<br />\n<br />\n美中經濟與安全審查委員會周三發表致送國會的年度報告，建議美國商務部考慮將香港和中國視為同一關稅區域，甚至推演至取消《美國-香港政策法》。事實上，倘若最終落實取消香港關係法，標普恐怕跌至個位數，美國此舉是搬起石頭砸自己的腳。<br />\n<br />\n所謂佔中令港股損失3500億元，同一道理，美國周三公佈此報告內容後，標普隨即大跌最多52點，納指<span style=\"color: red;\">暴跌</span>128點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。紐交所股票總市值為28.53萬億美元；納斯達克總市值11.86萬億美元。標普每跌一點，便等於名義財富消失了105億美元；納指每跌一點名義財富消失了16億美元。周三與周四美股賬面財富蒸發了7,508多億美元。<br />\n<br />\n相反，同一時間，港股上升了最多334點，港股總市值為30.13萬億港元，恒指是兩萬六點，恒指每升一點，便等於名義財富增加了11.5億港元，周三與周四港股賬面財富增長了3,841多億元，這是市場即各投資者對未來局面的一個初步評估。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只是稍為發表報告放風取消關係法，立即導致美股暴跌而港股上升，假設報告僅及真正取消法例的一成威力，一旦真正取消香港關係法，而港股隨時暴升3340點，接近重上三萬點水平，重新撻著牛市。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港股重上三萬點絕非天荒夜談</span></span>，因「美中經濟與安全審查委員報告」被港股市場認為是個正面事件，對今天及將來的營商環境都有利。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一旦取消與美國的關係，不排除發展至令到我國更加信任或扶持香港，在取消香港關係法後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我國只需派遣北水3萬億元來港買股票，便足以掃起港股三千點，</span></span>以我國13億人口計算，救港北水資金每名中國人僅付出2044元人民幣，對我的國而言實在太小數目。</span></span>事實上，近期港股觸底後有強力支持，加上騰訊（700）業績被市場認為是好，本身已有反彈條件。<br />\n<br />\n至於標普點解要見個位數？因為近期股評界潮流興閒閒地都跌八成，雖然一般內文冇交代原因，但標題唔寫見個位數，呢篇文恐怕冇人見到，所以惟有將標普500指數首站目標價定喺9點，現價計跌99.67%，順應潮流，冇乜特別原因。<br />\n<br />\n高明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bigricetea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbigricetea%2F&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2f612594\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bigricetea/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=628eafce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181118/58927809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927809&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5e8da6e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927809&h=725d8aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181118/58927809</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4e3b7686d1b9d26e972b5b851a7967c35c3854","tid":906643,"uid":55200,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"76b30fb4726fb947a7f793b328dc05a3bf7660bf","tid":906643,"uid":48083,"like