target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181008/20517331</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181022/20527989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181022%2F20527989&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d707d2c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181022%2F20527989&h=7955e175\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181022/20527989</a>"},{"pid":"7cb4f81b66c0934239f7a55f841b915d6a628f40","tid":906643,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"如果係咁更加要全力支持取消關係法，可能不費一粒子彈輕鬆打低美帝喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6e55a5203eaba467ae7ad86d0abc1b0487173","tid":906643,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"笑到最後：小米合理價16.4元 - 高明<br />\n<br />\n小米現價計回落至16.4元，再無限橫行一段長時間，中央先會覺得合理。小米追揸沽，高明會企喺阿爺嘅同一邊！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180716/20451369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451369&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=097a5ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451369&h=902185d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180716/20451369</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f626e624df8bc1b9fe1795f04f740a21cc34778d","tid":906643,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:44:15.000Z","msg":"美股日日都暴升暴跌，好惡佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8889068d577c8ac737a8e39ef31b5804686d5c7b","tid":906643,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"舊文參考<br />\n較傾向係真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑到最後：死亡變黃金的契機 - 高明<br />\n<br />\n2018-07-30<br />\n<br />\n7.4K<br />\n投資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯高明傾向相信，港股將會有一個黃金交叉的契機，背後原因只有三個字：定價權。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯港股入面有好多中資股，長期被外資沽空，外國勢力不想中國強大，所以令中國估值偏低，只要北水湧港，狂買港股，炒高估值，便可取回港股定價權。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月初美股小股災，港股成交回落至700億元左右，明顯外資已被中資定價權震懾，交返個場出嚟，任由我國定價。不過，我國傳媒對定價權嘅論述同步減少，恒指亦已回到去年11月「勝利宣言」時水平。<br />\n<br />\n50天線跌穿250天線看似係死亡交叉，但只要我國北水不只有嘴炮，而係真金白銀南下來港掃高港股，告訴全球資金，外國人給予港股嘅估值係錯，中國人買落去嘅估值先係啱，現時恒指市盈率僅12倍，相對標普24倍，明顯被嚴重睇低，中資北水應立即來港掃港股，炒上合理水平。<br />\n<br />\n至於一般散戶點睇北水真係有心爭奪定價權，再炒高港股？根據該篇勝利宣言，「一旦某地區某外族移民佔比超過了10%，將直接改變該地區的生態與話語權分配」，只要港股通資金流入佔一成，即淨流入約70億元，便等同北水再度湧港，然後連續10日大額流入，相信我國穩奪定價權。到時值得追入，因為牛市已重新撻着。<br />\n<br />\n高明<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/bigricetea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fbigricetea&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f1ff86cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/bigricetea</a> <br />\n本欄逢周一刊出<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180730/20464125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464125&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=eba9fb41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464125&h=ff830e93\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180730/20464125</a>"}]}